，你們僅僅吃了兩坨屎就為咱們國家貢獻了 1 個億的 GDP ！&rdquo;"},{"pid":"7854373d1e2949f03470133df10f0bf3814a3ab1","tid":1857721,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:12:47.000Z","msg":"支國地方政府啲財政數據仲屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70631669403b521999a1cd1c8d2e4aa231cf1655","tid":1857721,"uid":60831,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:13:54.000Z","msg":"靠口罩同殯儀業撐起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c6ef51ad8539830f4880a3bbf3b064b8977914","tid":1857721,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:14:07.000Z","msg":"無事啦，死幾隻支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好唔記得印銀紙買美貨呀"},{"pid":"b8d52ca95c5e4c567469c88ae73cd9cfda0d1a8e","tid":1857721,"uid":101307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:14:33.000Z","msg":"武漢啲樓唔要得啦 咁多病毒 鏟左佢再起過啲gdp話黎就黎啦"},{"pid":"359ddf46305f7a5272f1e086aeed44b309f4065b","tid":1857721,"uid":181418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:15:30.000Z","msg":"預測<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6f78307fa9be3218af1cebf84cc52b3c69e770","tid":1857721,"uid":280538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8117e88b51fca6dca31464aca40ef584d328204","tid":1857721,"uid":325556,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:10:14.000Z","msg":"殯儀業利好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3364da16139c35d53a76b29323554787c5c48e6c","tid":1857721,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:19:59.000Z","msg":"打完杖經濟會高速增長<br />\n今次瘟疫都一樣<img src